snippet.title: Road Maintenance Simulator | Official Trailer English | Aerosoft
snippet.description:
OUT NOW | https://strassenmeisterei.aerosoft.com/

Experience the everyday life in a German street maintenance service and complete a variety of realistic tasks in the area of road construction and maintenance! Choose between 30 extensive missions with complex and intervowen tasks and use unique vehicles as well as various tools for your work.

For more news and information follow us: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Aerosoft/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/AerosoftGmbH
